data.description: This spacious and inviting family home boasts a prime location in Kingsland, close to the Base, shopping centers, and schools. Offering a total of 5 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, and 2 versatile areas ideal for family gatherings, this residence provides ample space for comfortable living. The open concept kitchen seamlessly connects to the family room, creating a welcoming atmosphere filled with natural light. The private backyard overlooks a lovely pond, adding tranquility to the outdoor space. Upstairs, a large loft area complements 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, providing additional living. A bedroom and full bathroom on the main floor offer convenience and accessibility. The home is tastefully decorated, featuring notable amenities such as a large soaking tub in the Primary/Master bathroom, granite countertops in the kitchen, charming board and batten decoration in the living/dining room, and attractive tile and flooring throughout. With thoughtful design elements and plenty of room for everyone to enjoy their own cozy spaces, this home promises a comfortable and enjoyable lifestyle for the entire family.
